  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/89d30837c3ab4f6ee427e95dac5d27ff.avif?t=1652928531\" width=630 height=215 /></span><br>这是个视觉小说类游戏。<br>游戏风格：悬疑解谜，暴风雪山庄。<br>情节紧张，结局让人意想不到。<br>适合喜欢紧张刺激，沉浸体验的玩家。<br>文字量70万字，游戏时长近20小时。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/d5d409dca19c02bbdb08aa87652d5ed5.webp?t=1652928531\" width=630 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/ef775881995ccdf2d47643461cb6d88a.avif?t=1652928531\" width=500 height=281 /></span><br>雪之本境，常年冰封，自成一境。<br>2011年10月，大一学生端贤冲与女友江城雪来到”雪境旅店“打工。<br>随后遭遇雪暴，与其他人一起困于雪山中。<br>大雪迟迟未见停息迹象，众人随即打消了下山的念头。<br>期待依靠旅店内的供暖与食物来度过这场天灾。<br>但他们还没有来得及接受眼前的灾难，随后旅店的食物又神秘失踪。<br>你将亲自逆转绝境。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/e290440c89176552477dbbf09b6f00de.webp?t=1652928531\" width=630 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/547653ff3c1c41e4aad04a0b11536009.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>端贤冲</strong>「桀骜固执的大学生」男主角（玩家扮演）<br>原本只是和女友江城雪来到“雪境旅店”打工，却碰上了数日难息的雪暴。<br>面对种种天灾和人性的挑战，他希望用自己最朴素的原则来保护所爱的人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/4f8ec7a241fd4cbdae47c2c743e60de3.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>江城雪</strong>「温柔浪漫的女友」<br>原本只是和男友端贤冲一起来到“雪境旅店”打工，却碰上了数日难息的雪暴。<br>生性朴素手无缚鸡之力的她，独自一人将很难存活。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/9388fbc9d2fb0e6cb7a22390046855b1.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>归海枫</strong>「青梅竹马少女」<br>比端贤冲和江城雪提前几日来到雪境旅店打工的少女，自称是前辈。<br>最喜欢捉弄端贤冲，原来二人竟然是儿时的玩伴。<br>二人就在这座雪山中重逢，不知是命运安排还是境主的阴谋。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/b4bec1cff4db423719812e27df125afd.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>白悠悠</strong>「天才幽灵少女」<br>平时并不多说话，一旦聊到自己喜欢的东西则会滔滔不绝。<br>有着神话般的满分科目记录。<br>知识和分析能力属于旅人中的上等水准。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/ad6d86f92c4949aac2cfb3cd0ca23b5e.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>季愁然</strong>「内向寡言少女」<br>一直都不知道为什么会上山的旅客，看面相应该是只有18岁。<br>平时沉默寡言，面对众人更是一言不发。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/638b9ffd208f4f21db2b68cf98404abb.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>鸾渊</strong>「理性戒备女子」<br>与自己的新老公“叔桐山”一起来到雪境旅店度假。<br>拥有成熟女性的气质。<br>尽管刻意的压抑，但仍对陌生人有着很强的戒备心。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/9a0a2254ac12591195b6987800d20a44.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>雪中少女</strong>「解境篇新角色」<br>端贤冲发现于雪之本境的幻象，来去无踪。<br>这位雪中的少女，究竟是幻觉还是真实存在？<br>她的出现究竟是好是坏？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/911a587ec92413d4a2e88cd4e9df25e8.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>常舍青</strong>「谨慎严肃的店长」<br>曾经是知名的登山冲锋队长，攀登过无数雪峰。<br>然而不知道为什么近期突然做起了旅店生意。<br>生性谨慎，待人冷漠。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/649f9218f1b504084c233f36289fdfa0.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>叔桐山</strong>「温和友善的大叔」<br>外柔内刚，充满着理想与浪漫的情怀。<br>目前是某公司的执行总裁也是店长常舍青的登山队友。<br>容易受环境影响，而且并无解决之法。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/64488635716fb99c40104c6f567317c5.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>成启言</strong>「资深的当地向导」<br>当地向导，同时负责旅店后勤保障的工作。家有儿女，为人直爽坦率。<br>对外地游客十分热情，当然他的热情与你购买的特产数成正比。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/d2c13ecef2cc2062519e9f471c4a3b4d.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>贺松原</strong>「孤高自傲的游客」<br>某公司的信息技术员，多疑，悲观，对任何人都保持距离，并喜欢无端挑衅，挖苦别人。<br>尽管如此但技术实力不容置疑。之前曾经是常舍青手下的通信人员。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/e62da7983c53e6cd95c9a521f77369ab.webp?t=1652928531\" width=630 height=30 /></span><br>游戏分为<strong>「创境篇」</strong>和<strong>「解境篇」</strong>两部分，两者互为<strong>「前后篇」</strong>关系。<br>请先完成<strong>「创境篇」</strong>的剧情，再完成<strong>「解境篇」</strong>的剧情，以获得完成的剧情体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/4cc50a722af2e933b49237aa50f11f55.avif?t=1652928531\" width=500 height=281 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/dc2afa50ebae7d45a145254bdce6459f.avif?t=1652928531\" width=500 height=281 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/555513e17c84b0216247c15ab8f02381.avif?t=1652928531\" width=500 height=281 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/39a58c7c19b582a057b65e5abc8a367c.webp?t=1652928531\" width=630 height=30 /></span><br>SP-time官方微博： SP-time制作组 <br>bilibili官方账号：SP-time制作组<br>SP-time 交流和售后群：109907670<br><a href=\"mailto:合作和售后邮箱：SP_time@sina.com\">合作和售后邮箱：SP_time@sina.com</a>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/89d30837c3ab4f6ee427e95dac5d27ff.avif?t=1652928531\" width=630 height=215 /></span><br>这是个视觉小说类游戏。<br>游戏风格：悬疑解谜，暴风雪山庄。<br>情节紧张，结局让人意想不到。<br>适合喜欢紧张刺激，沉浸体验的玩家。<br>文字量70万字，游戏时长近20小时。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/d5d409dca19c02bbdb08aa87652d5ed5.webp?t=1652928531\" width=630 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/ef775881995ccdf2d47643461cb6d88a.avif?t=1652928531\" width=500 height=281 /></span><br>雪之本境，常年冰封，自成一境。<br>2011年10月，大一学生端贤冲与女友江城雪来到”雪境旅店“打工。<br>随后遭遇雪暴，与其他人一起困于雪山中。<br>大雪迟迟未见停息迹象，众人随即打消了下山的念头。<br>期待依靠旅店内的供暖与食物来度过这场天灾。<br>但他们还没有来得及接受眼前的灾难，随后旅店的食物又神秘失踪。<br>你将亲自逆转绝境。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/e290440c89176552477dbbf09b6f00de.webp?t=1652928531\" width=630 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/547653ff3c1c41e4aad04a0b11536009.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>端贤冲</strong>「桀骜固执的大学生」男主角（玩家扮演）<br>原本只是和女友江城雪来到“雪境旅店”打工，却碰上了数日难息的雪暴。<br>面对种种天灾和人性的挑战，他希望用自己最朴素的原则来保护所爱的人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/4f8ec7a241fd4cbdae47c2c743e60de3.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>江城雪</strong>「温柔浪漫的女友」<br>原本只是和男友端贤冲一起来到“雪境旅店”打工，却碰上了数日难息的雪暴。<br>生性朴素手无缚鸡之力的她，独自一人将很难存活。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/9388fbc9d2fb0e6cb7a22390046855b1.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>归海枫</strong>「青梅竹马少女」<br>比端贤冲和江城雪提前几日来到雪境旅店打工的少女，自称是前辈。<br>最喜欢捉弄端贤冲，原来二人竟然是儿时的玩伴。<br>二人就在这座雪山中重逢，不知是命运安排还是境主的阴谋。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/b4bec1cff4db423719812e27df125afd.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>白悠悠</strong>「天才幽灵少女」<br>平时并不多说话，一旦聊到自己喜欢的东西则会滔滔不绝。<br>有着神话般的满分科目记录。<br>知识和分析能力属于旅人中的上等水准。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/ad6d86f92c4949aac2cfb3cd0ca23b5e.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>季愁然</strong>「内向寡言少女」<br>一直都不知道为什么会上山的旅客，看面相应该是只有18岁。<br>平时沉默寡言，面对众人更是一言不发。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/638b9ffd208f4f21db2b68cf98404abb.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>鸾渊</strong>「理性戒备女子」<br>与自己的新老公“叔桐山”一起来到雪境旅店度假。<br>拥有成熟女性的气质。<br>尽管刻意的压抑，但仍对陌生人有着很强的戒备心。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/9a0a2254ac12591195b6987800d20a44.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>雪中少女</strong>「解境篇新角色」<br>端贤冲发现于雪之本境的幻象，来去无踪。<br>这位雪中的少女，究竟是幻觉还是真实存在？<br>她的出现究竟是好是坏？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/911a587ec92413d4a2e88cd4e9df25e8.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>常舍青</strong>「谨慎严肃的店长」<br>曾经是知名的登山冲锋队长，攀登过无数雪峰。<br>然而不知道为什么近期突然做起了旅店生意。<br>生性谨慎，待人冷漠。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/649f9218f1b504084c233f36289fdfa0.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>叔桐山</strong>「温和友善的大叔」<br>外柔内刚，充满着理想与浪漫的情怀。<br>目前是某公司的执行总裁也是店长常舍青的登山队友。<br>容易受环境影响，而且并无解决之法。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/64488635716fb99c40104c6f567317c5.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>成启言</strong>「资深的当地向导」<br>当地向导，同时负责旅店后勤保障的工作。家有儿女，为人直爽坦率。<br>对外地游客十分热情，当然他的热情与你购买的特产数成正比。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/d2c13ecef2cc2062519e9f471c4a3b4d.avif?t=1652928531\" width=220 height=220 /></span><br><strong>贺松原</strong>「孤高自傲的游客」<br>某公司的信息技术员，多疑，悲观，对任何人都保持距离，并喜欢无端挑衅，挖苦别人。<br>尽管如此但技术实力不容置疑。之前曾经是常舍青手下的通信人员。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/e62da7983c53e6cd95c9a521f77369ab.webp?t=1652928531\" width=630 height=30 /></span><br>游戏分为<strong>「创境篇」</strong>和<strong>「解境篇」</strong>两部分，两者互为<strong>「前后篇」</strong>关系。<br>请先完成<strong>「创境篇」</strong>的剧情，再完成<strong>「解境篇」</strong>的剧情，以获得完成的剧情体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/4cc50a722af2e933b49237aa50f11f55.avif?t=1652928531\" width=500 height=281 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/dc2afa50ebae7d45a145254bdce6459f.avif?t=1652928531\" width=500 height=281 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/555513e17c84b0216247c15ab8f02381.avif?t=1652928531\" width=500 height=281 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908250/extras/39a58c7c19b582a057b65e5abc8a367c.webp?t=1652928531\" width=630 height=30 /></span><br>SP-time官方微博： SP-time制作组 <br>bilibili官方账号：SP-time制作组<br>SP-time 交流和售后群：109907670<br><a href=\"mailto:合作和售后邮箱：SP_time@sina.com\">合作和售后邮箱：SP_time@sina.com</a>",
